                  <summary>I) Śǝrʿāta qǝddāse “Ordinary of the Mass” (fols. 3ra-26vb)&#xD;
II) Anaphoras (fols. 26vb-98rb)&#xD;
III) Daily Office Prayers and litanies (fols. 98rb-113rb)&#xD;
III-1) Ṣalota kidān za-śalastu gizeyāt “Covenant Prayer of the Three Hours” (fols. 98rb-106va)&#xD;
III-2) Litanies (fols. 106vb-113rb)&#xD;
&#xD;
Additiones 1-2.</summary>
