                     <list>
                        <item xml:id="a1"> <locus target="#48ra">f. 48ra</locus>: Ownership note (?). <quote xml:lang="gez"> <locus target="48ra">48ra</locus>: አቡነ፡ ወልደ፡ አነንያ፡ ወምስለ፡ አመቱ፡ ወለተ፡ ሥላሴ፡</quote>
                           <quote xml:lang="en"/>
                           The note is written in deep brown ink and mentions <roleName type="title">ʾabuna</roleName> Walda ʾAnänya, possibly an owner of the book, and his servant Walatta Śǝllāse.
                        </item>
                        <item xml:id="a2"> <locus target="#113ra">f. 113ra</locus>-vb: excerpt from Mäftǝḥe śǝray or ʾasmat-prayer. <quote xml:lang="gez"> <locus target="113ra">113ra</locus>: በስመ፡ አብ፡ በል፡ መፍዝዝ፡ አፍዝዝ፡ መደንግዝ፡ አደንግዝ፡ አደንዝዝ፡ በኢያኤል፡ ስምከ፡ …</quote>
                           <quote xml:lang="en"/>
                           The note is written in greyish-brown ink. Text on <locus target="113va">113va</locus> is illegible.
                        </item>
                        <item xml:id="e1">- Omitted letters or words inserted interlineally in small script: e.g., <locus target="10rb">10rb</locus>, 49rb, 70ra, 107ra.&#xD;
- Immediate correction indicated by thin red lines above and below the word: <locus target="42ra">42ra</locus>.&#xD;
- Erasures marked with thin black and red lines: e.g., <locus target="31ra">31ra</locus>, 46rb, 49vb, 67vb, 89vb.&#xD;
- Corrections written over erasures in the main hand: <locus target="42ra">42ra</locus>, 49ra, 51rb. &#xD;
- The scribe used compressed script: <locus target="28rb">28rb</locus>.&#xD;
- Lacunae (spaces for names left unfilled): e.g., <locus target="55ra">55ra</locus>, 67vb.&#xD;
- Clues for the rubricator: e.g., <locus target="57va">57va</locus>, 72va, 96ra.&#xD;
- Part of the line is taken down: <locus target="48rb">48rb</locus>.&#xD;
- Excerpt of an unidentified text on <locus from="1ra" to="2ra">1ra-2ra</locus>.</item>
                     </list>
